# Deployment

- Server: Render free tier (Oregon), keep-alive ping every 10 min
- Build: `pip install yt-dlp && apt-get install -y ffmpeg || true && npm install && npm run build`
- Env vars: `syncbeat-secrets` group in Render dashboard
- Client API URL: set in `client/app.json` → `extra.apiUrl`
- Push notifications only work in `eas build` builds, not Expo Go

## Server Environment Variables

| Var | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `JWT_SECRET` | JWT signing |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Neon PostgreSQL (pooled connection string) |
| `REDIS_URL` | Upstash Redis (`rediss://` TLS) |
| `R2_ACCOUNT_ID`, `R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID`, `R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY` | Cloudflare R2 |
| `R2_BUCKET_NAME` | `syncbeat-tracks` |
| `R2_PUBLIC_URL` | Public R2 CDN URL |
| `RESEND_API_KEY`, `FROM_EMAIL` | Email (OTP) |
| `RENDER_EXTERNAL_URL` | Auto-set by Render, keep-alive ping |
